      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "And in the days of Saul they made war with the Hagarites.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—The great extension of the tribe in an easterly direction took place in the reign of Saul, the first king of Israel. Bela and his clan victoriously fought with the Hagarites (Heb., ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
