            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". The Belaites occupied the territory of the Hagarites.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Throughout all the east land of Gilead.—Rather, on the whole eastern side or border of Gilead. This includes the new settlements of Bela beyond the border.",
